text: Sven Ranck (1616–1684) was a Swedish statesman. Between 1678 and 1684, he served as the Governor of Halland County. He was the owner from 1674 to 1731 of the Marieberg residence in Bohuslän. == External links == * http://www.marberger.se/marieberg/marieberg.pdf Category:Governors of Halland County Category:Swedish nobility Category:1616 births Category:1684 deaths Category:17th-century Swedish politicians
